object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct policyreinsplacement.SystemId, policyreinsplacement.ParentId, policyreinsplacement.CMMContainer, policyreinsplacement.Id, policyreinsplacement.PlacementId, policyreinsplacement.ReinsuranceType, policyreinsplacement.StartLimitAmt, policyreinsplacement.PlacementAmt, policyreinsplacement.TreatyContract, policyreinsplacement.PlacementPct, policyreinsplacement.PremiumAmt, policyreinsplacement.TreatyTypeCd, policyreinsplacement.CommissionAmt, policyreinsplacement.CommissionPct, policyreinsplacement.Comments, policyreinsplacement.TransactionCommissionAmt, policyreinsplacement.StatusCd, policyreinsplacement.LossCalculationTypeCd, policyreinsplacement.BasePremiumAmt, policyreinsplacement.PrevFinalAmt, policyreinsplacement.WrittenPremiumAmt, policyreinsplacement.PrevWrittenAmt, policyreinsplacement.AutomaticRecoveryAdjustmentInd, policyreinsplacement.BaseWrittenPremiumAmt, policyreinsplacement.BaseWrittenPremiumToDateAmt, policyreinsplacement.PremiumWrittenAmt, policyreinsplacement.PrevPremiumWrittenAmt, policyreinsplacement.PremiumPct, policyreinsplacement.CededProRateInd, policyreinsplacement.LossCalculationLevel, policyreinsplacement.RowId 
FROM
 policyreinsplacement 
where systemid in 
(select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans 
where concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt' 
and cmmcontainer='Policy' ) 
and cmmcontainer='Policy'
